com.vector.cfg.model.groovy.api

Interface IModelReadApiEntryPoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMdfReadApi

    @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public interface IModelReadApiEntryPoint
extends IMdfReadApi
    IModelReadApiEntryPoint is the entry point for MDF model read access.
    The MDF model read access API is the entry point for convenient AUTOSAR model read access. It also provides a generic read API to the MDF data model.

    (c) Copyright Vctr Informatik GmbH. All Rights Reserved.
